page.title: 05Home life.
page.content:
{A day in Julie's life, conc.} After that I have a drink, then we have tea. After tea I practise my piano. I am going in for an exam. Then I watch some more television. My favourite female television presenter is Sue Robbie and my favourite male is Michael Praed, who is Robin in the television series "Robin Hood of Sherwood Forest". Sue Robbie hosts a quiz game called "Connections". Then I have supper and go to bed. I like reading and sometimes read in bed. I go to bed at about half past nine.
JULIE ERASMUSON
